<%- include('partials/header'); -%>

    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg mt-28">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-blue-500">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="faq-item mb-4">
            <div class="faq-toggle flex justify-between items-center p-4 bg-gray-100 rounded-lg">
                <span class="font-semibold">How does our platform determine the best travel routes?</span>
                <span class="toggle-icon font-extrabold">+</span>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-content hidden p-4">
                <p>Our platform analyzes data from various Indian airports to provide the most efficient travel routes.
                    We use real-time data and sophisticated algorithms to ensure that you get the best travel times and
                    costs.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item mb-4">
            <div class="faq-toggle flex justify-between items-center p-4 bg-gray-100 rounded-lg">
                <span class="font-semibold">What is Dijkstra's algorithm and how does it work?</span>
                <span class="toggle-icon font-extrabold">+</span>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-content hidden p-4">
                <p>Dijkstra's algorithm is used to find the shortest path between nodes in a graph. On our platform, it
                    calculates the minimum travel time and cost between airports, considering both direct and indirect
                    routes.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item mb-4">
            <div class="faq-toggle flex justify-between items-center p-4 bg-gray-100 rounded-lg">
                <span class="font-semibold">How do we handle indirect flights?</span>
                <span class="toggle-icon font-extrabold">+</span>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-content hidden p-4">
                <p>If there is no direct flight between your source and destination, our platform will find the best
                    route through intermediate airports, ensuring seamless travel planning.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item mb-4">
            <div class="faq-toggle flex justify-between items-center p-4 bg-gray-100 rounded-lg">
                <span class="font-semibold">Can I see the travel cost and time for each route?</span>
                <span class="toggle-icon font-extrabold">+</span>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-content hidden p-4">
                <p>Yes, our platform provides detailed information on the travel cost and time for each route, allowing
                    you to choose the most efficient and cost-effective option.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        // Select DOM elements
        const mobileMenuButton = document.querySelector('button[type="button"]');
        const mobileMenu = document.querySelector('.lg\\:hidden[role="dialog"]');
        const closeMenuButton = mobileMenu.querySelector('button[type="button"]');

        // Ensure the mobile menu is hidden on page load
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
            mobileMenu.classList.add('hidden');
        });

        // Toggle the visibility of the mobile menu
        function toggleMenu() {
            mobileMenu.classList.toggle('hidden');
        }

        // Add event listeners for open and close actions
        mobileMenuButton.addEventListener('click', toggleMenu);
        closeMenuButton.addEventListener('click', toggleMenu);

        // FAQs toggle working
        document.querySelectorAll('.faq-toggle').forEach(toggle => {
            toggle.addEventListener('click', () => {
                const content = toggle.nextElementSibling;
                content.classList.toggle('hidden');
                const icon = toggle.querySelector('.toggle-icon');
                icon.textContent = content.classList.contains('hidden') ? '+' : '-';
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>

</html>